                                    <div class="item_title">Hills</div>

                                    <div class="item_text">Kerala brings to you a magical tryst with nature through its various hills and hill stations. A majority of these places in Kerala are situated on the windward side of the majestic Western Ghats. Enjoy the long chain
                                        of lush mist-clad hill stations of Kerala and explore the various plantations, wildlife, flora and fauna that comprise an integral part of this experience.</div>
                                    <div class="item_more_link"><a href="/offers/<%=2%>">Read More</a></div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Item -->
                            <div class="item clearfix rating_5">
