                                    <div class="item_title">Picnic</div>

                                    <div class="item_text">Picnic spots adorn the landscape of our great state. Travellers can find a temporary abode in many natural locations across the length and breadth of Kerala. Picnickers tend to have trouble picking a spot! From dams
                                        and waterfalls to forests and natural reserves, Kerala is filled with places awaiting you. Grab your lunch basket and let's be on our way!
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="item_more_link"><a href="/offers/<%=9%>">Read More</a></div>
